%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User (Telegram)
    participant CC as 🗣️ Comms Claw
    participant RC as 🔍 Research Claw
    participant SC as 🕷️ Scraper Claw
    participant BC as 💰 Buyer Claw
    participant SL as 📦 Seller Claw
    participant DB as 🗄️ Inventory DB
    participant WEB as 🌐 Target Websites

    Note over U,SL: === PHASE 1: RESEARCH ===

    U->>RC: Send curated item list (links, preferences, constraints)
    RC->>RC: Validate links (non-eBay, correct category)
    RC->>RC: Confirm colors, sizes, options
    RC->>RC: Suggest similar trending items
    RC->>CC: Status: "Research complete - 10 items curated"
    CC->>U: 📋 Research Report via Telegram
    RC->>SC: Hand off validated item list

    Note over U,SL: === PHASE 2: SCRAPING ===

    loop Every 15 min (configurable)
        SC->>WEB: Check availability (via Selenium + Proxy)
        WEB-->>SC: Page response
        SC->>SC: Parse availability status
        SC->>SC: Extract current price
        SC->>SC: Take screenshot proof
        alt Status changed: Unavailable → Available
            SC->>CC: 🚨 ALERT: Item now available!
            CC->>U: ⚡ Telegram alert + screenshot + price
        end
        SC->>DB: Update item status in tracking sheet
    end
    SC->>SC: Compile availability report
    SC->>CC: Status: "Scrape complete - X items available"
    CC->>U: 📊 Full availability report
    SC->>BC: Hand off available items list

    Note over U,SL: === PHASE 3: BUYING ===

    U->>BC: Approve purchase (or auto-buy if configured)
    loop For each available item
        BC->>WEB: Navigate to item page
        BC->>BC: Add to cart
        BC->>BC: Set shipping address
        BC->>BC: Apply payment (Stripe)
        BC->>WEB: Complete checkout
        BC->>DB: Record: item, price, status="purchased", tracking#
        BC->>CC: Status: "Purchased [item] for $X"
        CC->>U: ✅ Purchase confirmation
    end
    BC->>SL: Hand off purchased items for resale

    Note over U,SL: === PHASE 4: SELLING ===

    SL->>DB: Get inventory of purchased items
    loop For each item to list
        SL->>SL: Calculate resale price (markup)
        SL->>SL: Create listing (photos, description)
        SL->>SL: List on Poshmark (via API/automation)
        SL->>DB: Update status="listed", list_price=$Y
        SL->>CC: Status: "Listed [item] at $Y"
    end

    alt Offer received on Poshmark
        SL->>SL: Evaluate offer vs minimum price
        alt Offer acceptable
            SL->>SL: Accept offer
            SL->>BC: Request: Update Poshmark shipping address to buyer
            SL->>DB: Update status="sold", sold_price=$Z
            SL->>CC: Status: "SOLD [item] for $Z 🎉"
            CC->>U: 💰 Sale notification + profit summary
        else Offer too low
            SL->>SL: Counter-offer or decline
            SL->>CC: Status: "Declined offer on [item]"
        end
    end
